Package GUIElements

Class TableRowGUI

java.lang.Object
GUIElements.GUIElement
GUIElements.TableRowGUI
public class TableRowGUI
extends GUIElement
Class that implements the table structure for the HTML table. It contains TableCellGUI's, and is contained by a TableGUI.
